                           <pdfaProperty:description>Values for Journal Article Version are one of the following:&#xA;AO = Author‚Äôs Original&#xA;SMUR = Submitted Manuscript Under Review&#xA;AM = Accepted Manuscript&#xA;P = Proof&#xA;VoR = Version of Record&#xA;CVoR = Corrected Version of Record&#xA;EVoR = Enhanced Version of Record</pdfaProperty:description>
